{"tid":832534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關稅生效倒數！支那赴美貨船暴增　運費創4年新高","createTime":"2018-09-22T20:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T00:44:48.000Z","uid":32511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a89baef61b3e1b32e93cf6c2b0894a794916bdb1","tid":832534,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T20:56:01.000Z","msg":"川普最新關稅周一起開徵，中國產品趕最後期限送往美國。<br />\n<br />\n川普對中國實施新一波關稅，周一正式生效，海運及空運總動員，<br />\n要搶時限將貨物從中國運到美國。<br />\n <br />\n影響所及，南韓現代商船（HMM）從中國前往美國的散裝船都是滿載，<br />\n加州各港口貨量暴增，太平洋航線的運費率來到4年新高。<br />\n <br />\n川普關稅擴大了中國黃金周前的趕貨效應，<br />\n中國製造商急著將玩具、腳踏車、汽車零件等送往美國。<br />\n <br />\n中國國際航空飛美的貨量也大增。<br />\n <br />\n鎮江億地光電照明（ED Opto Electrical Lighting Co.）8月底提前調度，<br />\n將１批車燈以海運送到洛杉磯，預定25天到達，就是為了趕上關稅的最後期限。<br />\n <br />\n此外，供應孩之寶公司的玩具製造商龍昌集團也表示，為了趕在關稅實施前交貨，<br />\n部分客戶已決定將運輸方式從海運改成空運。<br />\n <br />\n周一開始，輸往美國價值2000億美元的中國產品，將被課稅10%，年底會升到25%。<br />\n <br />\n根據海運顧問公司德魯里（Drewry）的世界貨櫃指數，上海至洛杉磯的即期貨運費率，<br />\n在9月13日為止當周已升到每40呎貨櫃2362美元，為2014年12月以來新高。<br />\n <br />\n彭博行業研究（Bloomberg Intelligence）分析師Rahul Kapoor表示：<br />\n <br />\n「關稅的搶時大賽開始」，<br />\n <br />\n他已聽說有貨被留在中國碼頭，原因是赴美貨船已經滿載。"},{"pid":"d4c6339d8512284afe2c19d29c2d9a582638dbd2","tid":832534,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T21:38:10.000Z","msg":"支那人隻腳真係好誠實"},{"pid":"1acd87df8547a56e10d998f843a1a4dc3edf4317","tid":832534,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T22:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7326b6e0b8326f4a732b89865e53a8ef65fc8e","tid":832534,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T23:50:17.000Z","msg":"鬥快賺完尾水"},{"pid":"a35fbd0e655046afee03d4a6ec4849e325c3276f","tid":832534,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T00:01:32.000Z","msg":"一節淡三墟！"},{"pid":"20e653255a27688a52025c5b1016f3667b3c4dd9","tid":832534,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4c6339d8512284afe2c19d29c2d9a582638dbd2","tid":832534,"uid":3241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T21:38:10.000Z","msg":"支那人隻腳真係好誠實"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T00:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d77e3cd9df3bd07a595caae2ccfaa65ce6f74df","tid":832534,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d7326b6e0b8326f4a732b89865e53a8ef65fc8e","tid":832534,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T23:50:17.000Z","msg":"鬥快賺完尾水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T00:21:30.000Z","msg":"到時個個走難了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bffe48bab2b91a181498b015020eb71ef6b1980","tid":832534,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T00:32:00.000Z","msg":"中國人好無骨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7df60a416d31783491bff99abaae05e8086797","tid":832534,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T00:44:48.000Z","msg":"貿易逆差再創新高<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}